    "name": "Hellmate",
    "steam_appid": 3225700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/de6a3e42b3778ebbc38fbb69d03d5503.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hellmate 是一款受国际象棋启发的 roguelike 牌组构建游戏，你需要通过卡牌创建强大的协同效应，尽可能快速地击败对方的国王棋子。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用卡牌来召唤棋子。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽可能高效地使用你的法力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/6d64b63cf3ae7b7f2df7ee1d6d8c61a4.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/6d64b63cf3ae7b7f2df7ee1d6d8c61a4.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/6d64b63cf3ae7b7f2df7ee1d6d8c61a4.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消灭敌方棋子，清除所有威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/145c463e7438fa18a65de770e2549306.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/145c463e7438fa18a65de770e2549306.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/145c463e7438fa18a65de770e2549306.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伤害点数仅影响国王。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽量在最短的回合时间内击败敌方国王，继续前进。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/42d3a7b89f731f6c87293601f75db8e9.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/42d3a7b89f731f6c87293601f75db8e9.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/42d3a7b89f731f6c87293601f75db8e9.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意国王的棋盘模式！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >围绕敌人制定你的策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/4891c9e5bf566bee1514b8c40f35c2c4.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/4891c9e5bf566bee1514b8c40f35c2c4.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/4891c9e5bf566bee1514b8c40f35c2c4.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/83ca4f8c656e025c402ec3d5ddb8b7c8.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用法术卡和棋子卡创建你独特的牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/ecfbf054427f7ab8c657f8552dd03071.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/ecfbf054427f7ab8c657f8552dd03071.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/ecfbf054427f7ab8c657f8552dd03071.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你选择的每张消耗品卡和 Joker 卡都能显著影响你的游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/988dbb7a4c41a25f6df26806c1ef2815.avif?t=1749912357\" width=609 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/a3d68594f896655499d5855f343937b1.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的Roguelike象棋体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E每一局都有 7 层随机生成的楼层，每层对应一种七宗罪主题。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/f6fb161efce1477ac148e45aacbe23ed.poster.avif?t=1749912357\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/f6fb161efce1477ac148e45aacbe23ed.webm?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225700/extras/f6fb161efce1477ac148e45aacbe23ed.mp4?t=1749912357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
